Manage your projects.
Commands can be run in whatever directory you're in as long as the user has set the current project.

Command list:

db
--
thor db:start  # Start database
thor db:stop   # Stop database

project
-------
thor project:create [PROJECTNAME]  # Creates project.
thor project:current               # Shows current project.
thor project:switch PROJECTNAME    # Switches current project

uportal
-------
thor uportal:ear   # ant deploy-ear
thor uportal:init  # ant initportal
thor uportal:war   # ant deploy-war